<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_48901bab-daf1-4c81-9e58-77b7a9035290" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>7.3.4</sptc><title id="_88708237-2b1e-492e-9263-bc02ac767dd9">Sarking</title><archive-num>2019: 3.5.2.4</archive-num><subclause id="_2e7e3be6-fbd3-44a1-af69-ce03b88f5a0e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_0218f1b7-48d1-4ad9-b047-7fb335a891b6">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Sarking must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_ed9255d6-d2d7-48df-a36b-c43017ec816c">be provided in accordance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/392_0.8.0.xml#_ba4d201d-9820-4c59-8252-673d9d5f4fb6" id="_1e1996ab-5fe7-44bd-ad99-dfa339302dea" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table 7.3.4</xref>; and</li><li id="_590b8c85-8bdf-4b19-9caf-1e80a832b3fa">comply with AS 4200.1 and be installed with—<ol><li>each adjoining sheet or roll being—<ol><li>overlapped not less than 150 mm; or</li><li>taped together; and</li></ol></li><li>sarking fixed to supporting members at not more than 300 mm centres; and</li><li>no sags more than 40 mm in the sarking.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/392_0.8.0.xml" graph="None" id="_ba4d201d-9820-4c59-8252-673d9d5f4fb6"><num xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" inv:access="external">7.3.4</num><title xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_11583b5b-52d8-4a83-a01d-0b04c107ad32" inv:access="external">Sarking requirements for tiled roofs</title><table xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_370bb86f-b34a-4a3e-a738-0fec34969e31" inv:access="external" keycol="1"><tgroup cols="2" inv:access="external"><colspec colname="001" colnum="1" colwidth="216.00*" inv:access="external"/><colspec colname="002" colnum="2" colwidth="216.00*" inv:access="external"/><thead inv:access="external"><row inv:access="external"><entry inv:access="external">Roof pitch</entry><entry inv:access="external">Maximum rafter/truss top chord length without sarking (mm) <sup id="_8d7bd740-c168-4757-ac4b-af98156316e2" inv:access="external">Note 1</sup></entry></row></thead><tbody inv:access="external"><row inv:access="external"><entry inv:access="external">&lt;18°</entry><entry inv:access="external">N/A <sup id="_0b3fd964-9cf1-4b00-90cb-dbb3dcd4e7e5" inv:access="external">Note 2</sup></entry></row><row inv:access="external"><entry inv:access="external">≥18° &lt;20°</entry><entry inv:access="external">4 500</entry></row><row inv:access="external"><entry inv:access="external">≥20° &lt;22°</entry><entry inv:access="external">5 500</entry></row><row inv:access="external"><entry inv:access="external">≥22°</entry><entry inv:access="external">6 000</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><desc-note xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_f98b9992-b7f0-415c-9e5b-a62d945e668f" inv:access="external"><ol inv:access="external" outputclass="numbered"><li id="_f2deb497-f0e2-4664-bd56-1aad19eba58a" inv:access="external">The maximum rafter/truss top chord length is measured from the topmost point of the rafter/truss i.e. the apex downwards. Where the maximum length is exceeded, sarking must be installed over the remainder of the rafter/truss top chord length towards the eave line of the roof, or equivalent where the building has no eaves.</li><li id="_eb89341a-bcd5-449f-aba0-c15c69e5250e" inv:access="external">All tiled roofs with a pitch less than 18 degrees must be provided with sarking, regardless of rafter/truss chord length.</li></ol></desc-note></table-reference><callout id="_785e32b0-7bfe-41aa-a1a3-29b9c933bc53"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Where sarking is also provided as <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1427_4.6.0.xml#_710062da-7211-491f-ad4c-b3f12b9b96bb" id="_9ccc43b6-7d13-45c2-ac94-0841c701387b" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">reflective insulation</xref> for the purpose of energy efficiency, Section 13 of the ABCB Housing Provisions contains <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_e36d435f-0e46-4887-ae6c-ec0350097812" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_265f469b-24b5-4d9f-a1ad-31d18c62ae6e" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> and the necessary airspaces adjoining the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1427_4.6.0.xml#_710062da-7211-491f-ad4c-b3f12b9b96bb" id="_344d0b51-0849-47e0-80bd-a0b9304ea1d6" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">reflective insulation</xref>.</p></callout></clause>